---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageDocument from '../../../components/PageDocument.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - ASMR Color Reveal Kids" backUrl="/en/asmr-color-reveal-kids/">
  <PageDocument title="Privacy Policy">
    <p class="text-muted">Last updated: January 2026</p>

    <p>ASMR Color Reveal Kids ("the App") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect and how we use it.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>The App collects minimal data to provide you with a great experience:</p>
    <ul class="custom-list">
        <li><strong>Game Progress:</strong> Your coloring progress, completed images, and earned coins are stored locally on your device.</li>
        <li><strong>Preferences:</strong> Settings like sound and haptic feedback preferences are stored locally on your device.</li>
        <li><strong>Purchase Information:</strong> If you make in-app purchases, the transaction is handled by Google Play. We only store whether you have unlocked premium features.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All your game data and preferences are stored <strong>locally on your device</strong>. We do not collect, transmit, or store your personal information on external servers.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>The App uses the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul class="custom-list">
        <li><strong>Google Play Billing:</strong> Processes in-app purchases securely. Google handles all payment information.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These services have their own privacy policies that govern their data collection practices.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>ASMR Color Reveal Kids is designed to be family-friendly. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. The App complies with COPPA (Children's Online Privacy Protection Act) guidelines.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have control over your data:</p>
    <ul class="custom-list">
        <li>Clear the App's data through your device settings to remove all locally stored information.</li>
        <li>Opt out of personalized advertisements in your device's privacy settings.</li>
        <li>Uninstall the App at any time to remove all associated data from your device.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 30px;">Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or the App, please contact us at:</p>
    <p><a href="mailto:android-support@neurodiv.dev">android-support@neurodiv.dev</a></p>
  </PageDocument>
</BaseLayout>
